import { Box, Grid, ImageList, ImageListItem, Paper, Stack, Typography } from "@material-ui/core";
import Masonry, { ResponsiveMasonry } from "react-responsive-masonry";



function AboutMe() {
    return (

        
        <ResponsiveMasonry
        columnsCountBreakPoints={{350: 1, 750: 2, 900: 2}}
    >
        <Masonry style={{margin:'auto', width:'60rem'}} gutter='1rem'>
           <Paper elevation={2} sx={{p:'0.3rem'}}>
               <Grid container>
                   <Grid item flexGrow='1'>
                       <Box sx={{width:'100%', display:'flex', justifyContent:'center', backgroundColor:'red'}}>
                           bb
                       </Box>
                   </Grid>
                   <Grid item flexGrow='1'>
                   <Box sx={{width:'100%', height:'16rem', display:'flex', justifyContent:'center', alignItems:'center', backgroundColor:'blu'}}>
                           <Typography sx={{fontSize:'1.5rem', fontFamily:'sans-serif', fontWeight:'600', color:'success.main'}}>
                               Brian Ojoh Mile
                           </Typography>
                       </Box>
                   </Grid>
               </Grid>
           </Paper>
        </Masonry>
    </ResponsiveMasonry>
    
    )
}

export default AboutMe;
